sentences.sContent: His writing style is now boring and outdated.
sentences.sCn: 他的写作风格如今已显得乏味而过时了。

sentences.sContent: ...I can’t seem to get anyone in the hospital to listen to my complaints and this outdated equipment is dangerous...

trans.tranOther: if something is outdated, it is no longer considered useful or effective, because something more modern exists
